      <title>Discover 同意就商家过度收费的集体诉讼达成和解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/discover-agrees-to-settle-credit-card-misclassification-claims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[同意被 Capital One Financial Corp. 收购的信用卡公司 Discover Financial Services 表示，已达成协议，以解决针对商家过度收费的集体诉讼。]]></description>
