    <item>
      <title>勒庞谴责竞争对手阻止极右翼政党掌权的行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-denounces-rivals-efforts-to-keep-far-right-from-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[极右翼领导人玛丽娜·勒庞严厉批评法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的中间派团体和左翼联盟联手阻止她领导的国民联盟党在法国立法选举第二轮也是最后一轮中获得绝对多数席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-denounces-rivals-efforts-to-keep-far-right-from-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 21:39:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果完成首个高级别国际货币基金组织贷款计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/congo-completes-first-ever-high-level-imf-loan-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总部位于华盛顿特区的国际货币基金组织周三宣布，世界第二大铜生产国刚果民主共和国历史上首次完成了国际货币基金组织的贷款计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/congo-completes-first-ever-high-level-imf-loan-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 21:31:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿美和阿布扎比国家石油公司正在考虑竞购天然气生产商 Santos</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/aramco-adnoc-are-said-to-consider-bids-for-gas-producer-santos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，沙特阿美公司和阿布扎比国家石油公司一直在分别研究对澳大利亚桑托斯有限公司的潜在收购，这两家中东能源巨头正寻求加大海外天然气投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/aramco-adnoc-are-said-to-consider-bids-for-gas-producer-santos</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 20:13:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在亚马逊的帮助下，Saks 所有者 Neiman 接近达成 26.5 亿美元交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/saks-owner-said-near-deal-to-buy-neiman-marcus-for-2-65-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，萨克斯第五大道 (Saks Fifth Avenue) 的所有者即将以 26.5 亿美元收购尼曼集团 (Neiman Marcus Group) - 这笔交易将合并美国两大高端百货连锁店，以期在增长放缓的行业中抢占更大的份额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/saks-owner-said-near-deal-to-buy-neiman-marcus-for-2-65-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 20:09:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选交易增多，全球市场警惕拜登退欧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/wall-street-on-alert-for-biden-exit-as-trump-win-trades-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿关于总统乔·拜登是否放弃竞选连任的激烈辩论正在蔓延到华尔街，交易员们正在将资金转移到美元、美国国债和其他可能受唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫影响的资产上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/wall-street-on-alert-for-biden-exit-as-trump-win-trades-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:53:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：疲软数据拖累美国收益率，股市创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一系列弱于预期的经济报告强化了美联储今年开始降息的理由后，华尔街交易员推高了股市，而债券收益率则下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 22:19:10 GMT</pubDate>
